Package org.neo4j.io.fs

Class PhysicalFlushableChecksumChannel

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.neo4j.io.fs.PhysicalFlushableChannel
      • org.neo4j.io.fs.PhysicalFlushableChecksumChannel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable, ChecksumWriter, FlushableChannel, FlushableChecksumChannel, WritableChannel, WritableChecksumChannel
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    PhysicalFlushableLogChannel
    public class PhysicalFlushableChecksumChannel
extends PhysicalFlushableChannel
implements FlushableChecksumChannel
    The main implementation of FlushableChannel. This class provides buffering over a simple StoreChannel and, as a side effect, allows control of the flushing of that buffer to disk.
